org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system

Class Finalizer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.system.Finalizer

  • public class Finalizer
extends java.lang.Object
    ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- // Finalization // // *Most* of the time finalization isn't going to be necessary, as we manually close using // reference counting. In .Net, we'd call GC.suppressFinalize() when that happens, but here // in Java we don't have that mechanism. Yet we want to minimize the number of finalization // calls that happen when they don't actually need to, as finalizable objects are significantly // more expensive than non-finalizable ones. Hence, the mechanism below. //----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
